### Provider Backend Smoke Test
### Use with VS Code REST Client or JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Update the variables below before running.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@providerId = bc5eac38-a1be-4edd-9e14-d246a3d8699b
@receiverRequestId = 36440d09-6abb-4c5e-81c4-e94f23a7f98b
@providerPostId = c6857425-64c3-4303-915b-3a167dd0210c
@transactionId = 31d6f553-d607-411a-b6d5-a7f4e91d5fdb
@transactionQrCode = NL-QR-VEG-0001

### 0. Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 1. Provider dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/impact/summary
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 2. Provider weekly ESG data
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/impact/weekly
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 3. Create a provider post
### 3a. Preview AI top 5 consumer matches
POST {{baseUrl}}/provider/matching/preview
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

{
  "title": "Buffet trua khach san (suat an)",
  "category": "Bữa ăn nấu sẵn",
  "weightKg": 28,
  "description": "Dong hop san, bao quan lanh",
  "address": "12 Le Loi, Quan 1, TP.HCM",
  "pickupWindow": "14:30 - 16:00 hom nay"
}

### 3b. Create a provider post
POST {{baseUrl}}/provider/posts
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

{
  "title": "Buffet trua khach san (suat an)",
  "category": "PREPARED_MEAL",
  "weightKg": 28,
  "description": "Dong hop san, bao quan lanh",
  "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546069901-ba9599a7e63c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=70",
  "address": "12 Le Loi, Quan 1, TP.HCM",
  "district": "Quan 1",
  "pickupWindow": "14:30 - 16:00 hom nay",
  "expiresInHours": 3
}

### 4. List my provider posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/posts
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 5. List my provider posts by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/posts?status=OPEN
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 6. Get one provider post
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/posts/{{providerPostId}}
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 7. Update one provider post
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/provider/posts/{{providerPostId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

{
  "title": "Buffet trua khach san (cap nhat)",
  "weightKg": 30,
  "pickupWindow": "15:00 - 17:00 hom nay",
  "description": "Cap nhat so luong va khung gio nhan"
}

### 8. View incoming requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/requests/incoming
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 9. View incoming requests filtered by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/requests/incoming?status=PENDING
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 10. Accept one request
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/provider/requests/{{receiverRequestId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

{
  "status": "ACCEPTED"
}

### 11. Reject one request
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/provider/requests/{{receiverRequestId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

{
  "status": "REJECTED"
}

### 12. View notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/notifications
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 13. View unread notifications only
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/notifications?unread=true
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 14. Mark one notification as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/provider/notifications/REPLACE_NOTIFICATION_ID/read
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### 15. Confirm a transaction by QR
POST {{baseUrl}}/provider/transactions/{{transactionId}}/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

{
  "qrCode": "{{transactionQrCode}}"
}

### 16. Soft-close one post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/provider/posts/{{providerPostId}}
x-user-id: {{providerId}}

### Suggested manual test order
### 1) Run health
### 2) Run impact summary to confirm provider id works
### 3) Create post
### 4) Preview matching to confirm top 5 consumers are returned
### 5) List posts and copy a post id into @providerPostId
### 6) Update / get the created post
### 7) If receiver-side seed data exists, inspect incoming requests
### 8) Accept one request and capture transaction id + qrCode from response
### 9) Confirm transaction
### 10) Check notifications and impact summary again
### 11) Soft-close a different OPEN post if needed
